subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Suzann Pettersen shot a five-under 67 in the Wegmans L.P.G.A. in Rochester to open a three-stroke lead over Morgan Pressel, Eun-Hee Ji and Inbee Park. The 28-year-old Pettersen, a five-time tour winner in 2007, is still looking for her first victory this season. Her bogey-free round Saturday got her to 14-under 202.
